'''Jason Dupree''' is Violet's lawyer.

==History==
Jason came to Violet and said that the medical board had agreed to re-visit her case.

They then went over all her patient files together, looking for success stories in patients she abruptly had to stop treatment. He said that with the cases the were able to compile, she had a very strong case.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
While working with Violet on her case, he asked her to get a meal with her at a sushi place. She told him she was married.

==Career==
He is a lawyer. Violet hired him to help her fight the medical board's ruling.
